Package frc.qefrc.qelib.led

Class LEDStrip

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.qefrc.qelib.led.LEDStrip
  • public class LEDStrip
extends Object
    LEDStrip is an abstraction over AddressableLED and AddressableLEDBuffer. It provide enhanced functionality for static colors and patterns

      • update

        public void update()
        Update the LED strip with the most recent LED Buffer data. This must be called semi frequently to keep the LEDs updated.

        Important: This method works best when called in a Subsystem periodic() method or the IterativeRobotBase.robotPeriodic() method.
